<t>CREATE TABLE Media (media_id INT PRIMARY KEY, title VARCHAR(255), type VARCHAR(50), published_date DATE)

CREATE TABLE MediaReviews (review_id INT PRIMARY KEY, media_id INT, user_id INT, rating INT, review_text TEXT, FOREIGN KEY (media_id) REFERENCES Media(media_id)</t><s>select title, rating from media inner join mediareviews on media.media_id = mediareviews.media_id inner join mediaauthors on media.media_id = mediaauthors.media_id where rating > 3</s>
<t>CREATE TABLE Media (media_id INT PRIMARY KEY, title VARCHAR(255), type VARCHAR(50), published_date DATE)

CREATE TABLE MediaReviews (review_id INT PRIMARY KEY, media_id INT, user_id INT, rating INT, review_text TEXT, FOREIGN KEY (media_id) REFERENCES Media(media_id)

CREATE TABLE MediaAuthors (media_id INT, author_id INT, FOREIGN KEY (media_id) REFERENCES Media(media_id), FOREIGN KEY (author_id) REFERENCES Authors(author_id)</t><s>SELECT title, rating FROM Media INNER JOIN MediaReviews ON Media.media_id = MediaReviews.media_id INNER JOIN MediaAuthors ON Media.media_id = MediaAuthors.media_id WHERE rating > 3</s>

CREATE TABLE Media_Directors (media_id INT, director_name VARCHAR(255), FOREIGN KEY (media_id) REFERENCES Media(id))

CREATE TABLE Media_Genres (media_id INT, genre_name VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (media_id) REFERENCES Media(id))</t><s>select * from media_actors</s>

CREATE TABLE Media_Actors (media_id INT, actor_name VARCHAR(255), FOREIGN KEY (media_id) REFERENCES Media(id))

CREATE TABLE Media_Genres (media_id INT, genre_name VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (media_id) REFERENCES Media(id))</t><s>SELECT media_id, actor_name FROM Media_Actors</s>

CREATE TABLE Media_Genres (media_id INT, genre_name VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (media_id) REFERENCES Media(id))</t><s>SELECT media_id, genre_name FROM Media_Genres</s>

CREATE TABLE Media_Directors (media_id INT, director_name VARCHAR(255), FOREIGN KEY (media_id) REFERENCES Media(id))</t><s>SELECT title, director_name, genre_name FROM Media, Media_Directors, Media_Genres WHERE Media.id = Media_Directors.media_id AND Media.id = Media_Genres.media_id</s>
<t>CREATE TABLE Media_Actors (media_id INT, actor_name VARCHAR(255), FOREIGN KEY (media_id) REFERENCES Media(id))

<t>CREATE TABLE media_content (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);


CREATE TABLE media_category (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_type (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_files (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);


CREATE TABLE media_tags (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);
</t><s>SELECT * FROM media_content;</s>

    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);

    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,

    description TEXT,

);

);

    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,

    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_files (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);


CREATE TABLE media_tags (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_content (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);


CREATE TABLE media_type (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);

    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_files (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);


CREATE TABLE media_content (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);


CREATE TABLE media_tags (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);

    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);


CREATE TABLE media_files (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);


CREATE TABLE media_tags (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_type (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_category (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);
</t><s>select * from media_content where title like '%example%';</s>

    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_tags (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_content (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);


CREATE TABLE media_files (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);

    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);

    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);

    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,

    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_content (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);


CREATE TABLE media_type (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_files (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);


CREATE TABLE media_category (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);

    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);


CREATE TABLE media_category (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_content (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);


CREATE TABLE media_type (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);

    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);


CREATE TABLE media_category (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_content (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);


CREATE TABLE media_tags (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);

    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);


CREATE TABLE media_tags (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_type (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_category (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_content (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);
</t><s>select * from media_category where category_name = 'movies';</s>

    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,

);

    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,

    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);


CREATE TABLE media_tags (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_content (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);

    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);

    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP

    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);


CREATE TABLE media_tags (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_type (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_files (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);


CREATE TABLE media_category (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);

    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);


CREATE TABLE media_type (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);

    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,

    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);

    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,

    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);

    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_type (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_files (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);


CREATE TABLE media_tags (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_content (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);
</t><s>SELECT file_name, file_size FROM media_files WHERE content_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';</s>

    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);

    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);

    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_files (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);


CREATE TABLE media_content (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);


CREATE TABLE media_category (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_tags (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);
</t><s>SELECT mc.title, mt.type_name FROM media_content mc INNER JOIN media_type mt ON mc.id = mt.id;</s>

    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);


CREATE TABLE media_content (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);


CREATE TABLE media_type (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);
</t><s>SELECT mc.title, mt.type_name FROM media_content mc INNER JOIN media_type mt ON mc.id = mt.id;</s>

    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);


CREATE TABLE media_category (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_type (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_tags (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_files (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);
</t><s>select mc.title, mf.file_name from media_content mc inner join media_files mf on mc.id = mf.content_id;</s>

    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);


CREATE TABLE media_tags (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_category (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_type (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);

    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);


CREATE TABLE media_tags (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_category (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_content (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);


CREATE TABLE media_type (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);
</t><s>SELECT mc.title, mf.file_name FROM media_content mc INNER JOIN media_files mf ON mc.id = mf.content_id;</s>

    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);

    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,

    file_size INT NOT NULL,

    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_content (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);


CREATE TABLE media_type (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_files (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);
</t><s>select mc.title, mt.type_name, mf.file_name from media_content mc inner join media_type mt on mc.id = mt.id inner join media_files mf on mc.id = mf.content_id;</s>

    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_content (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);


CREATE TABLE media_type (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_category (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_files (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);
</t><s>select mc.title, mt.type_name, mf.file_name from media_content mc inner join media_type mt on mc.id = mt.id inner join media_files mf on mc.id = mf.content_id;</s>
<t>CREATE TABLE media_tags (

    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);


CREATE TABLE media_tags (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_category (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_files (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);
</t><s>select mc.title, mcat.category_name from media_content mc left join media_category mcat on mc.id = mcat.id;</s>

    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_content (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);


CREATE TABLE media_type (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_files (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);


CREATE TABLE media_tags (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);
</t><s>SELECT mc.title, mtag.tag_name FROM media_content mc LEFT JOIN media_tags mtag ON mc.id = mtag.id;</s>

    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_category (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_content (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);


CREATE TABLE media_files (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);


CREATE TABLE media_tags (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);

    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_files (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);


CREATE TABLE media_content (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);
</t><s>select mc.title, mtag.tag_name from media_content mc left join media_tags mtag on mc.id = mtag.id;</s>

    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_type (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_category (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);
</t><s>select mc.title, mc.description, mt.type_name, mtag.tag_name from media_content mc inner join media_type mt on mc.id = mt.id inner join media_tags mtag on mc.id = mtag.id;</s>

    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);


CREATE TABLE media_content (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);
</t><s>SELECT mc.title, mc.description, mt.type_name, mtag.tag_name FROM media_content mc INNER JOIN media_type mt ON mc.id = mt.id INNER JOIN media_tags mtag ON mc.id = mtag.id;</s>

    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    tag_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_files (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_size INT NOT NULL,
    content_id UUID REFERENCES media_content(id),
);


CREATE TABLE media_content (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    publish_date TIMESTAMP
);


CREATE TABLE media_category (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);


CREATE TABLE media_type (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    type_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
);
</t><s>select mc.title, mc.description, mt.type_name, mtag.tag_name from media_content mc inner join media_type mt on mc.id = mt.id inner join media_tags mtag on mc.id = mtag.id;</s>
